---
// Editorial hero: full-bleed cream canvas, hairline rule, Instrument Serif italic.
---

<section class="hero">
	<div class="rule top" aria-hidden="true"></div>
	<div class="grid">
		<div class="meta">
			<p class="kicker">
				<span>№ 001</span>
				<span aria-hidden="true">—</span>
				<span>An Editorial Library</span>
			</p>
			<p class="folio">Volume I · Issue 1.0.0 · 2026</p>
		</div>

		<div class="copy">
			<h1>
				<span class="line one">Simple key-value</span>
				<span class="line two"><em>storage,</em></span>
				<span class="line three">for every backend</span>
				<span class="line four"><em>you actually use.</em></span>
			</h1>

			<p class="sub">
				A small interface over Redis, Postgres, SQLite, Mongo, Valkey, and seven
				other backends. TTL, namespaces, pluggable serialization, encryption,
				compression — without the framework tax.
			</p>

			<div class="actions">
				<a class="cta" href="/docs/getting-started/">
					Read the docs
					<span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
				</a>
				<a class="cta secondary" href="/adapters/">Browse adapters</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<aside class="aside">
			<p class="aside-label">Editor's note</p>
			<p class="aside-body">
				Storely 1.0.0 ships twelve storage adapters across three maturity tiers.
				Pick what fits — start with SQLite locally, swap in Redis or Postgres
				when traffic arrives. The API stays the same.
			</p>
			<p class="aside-patron">
				Maintained by one person. If it saved you a weekend,
				<a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/ritesh.rana" rel="noopener">consider a coffee →</a>
			</p>
		</aside>
	</div>
	<div class="rule bottom" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</section>

<style>
	.hero {
		position: relative;
		padding: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 5rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
	}

	.rule {
		height: 1px;
		background: var(--rule);
		margin-inline: var(--margin);
	}

	.rule.bottom {
		margin-top: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
	}

	.grid {
		max-width: 1320px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem) var(--margin) 0;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 4fr) minmax(0, 1.5fr);
		grid-template-areas:
			"meta meta"
			"copy aside";
		gap: var(--gutter);
		row-gap: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
	}

	@media (max-width: 880px) {
		.grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			grid-template-areas:
				"meta"
				"copy"
				"aside";
		}
	}

	.meta {
		grid-area: meta;
		display: flex;
		align-items: baseline;
		justify-content: space-between;
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: var(--step--2);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: var(--tracking-caps);
		color: var(--ink-faint);
	}

	.kicker {
		display: inline-flex;
		gap: 0.7rem;
		align-items: baseline;
	}

	.copy {
		grid-area: copy;
		max-width: 22ch;
	}

	h1 {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: var(--step-7);
		line-height: 0.96;
		letter-spacing: var(--tracking-display);
		color: var(--ink);
	}

	h1 .line {
		display: block;
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateY(0.4em);
		animation: rise var(--dur-slow) var(--ease-out) forwards;
	}

	h1 .one {
		animation-delay: 60ms;
	}
	h1 .two {
		animation-delay: 160ms;
		padding-left: 0.4em;
	}
	h1 .three {
		animation-delay: 280ms;
	}
	h1 .four {
		animation-delay: 400ms;
		padding-left: 1.4em;
	}

	h1 em {
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	@keyframes rise {
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}

	.sub {
		margin-top: 1.4rem;
		max-width: 36rem;
		font-size: var(--step-1);
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: var(--ink-soft);
	}

	.actions {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		gap: 2rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.cta {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: var(--step-1);
		color: var(--accent);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
		padding-bottom: 4px;
		display: inline-flex;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		align-items: baseline;
		transition: border-width var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out);
	}

	.cta:hover {
		border-bottom-width: 2px;
	}

	.cta.secondary {
		color: var(--ink-soft);
		border-bottom-color: var(--rule);
	}

	.cta.secondary:hover {
		color: var(--ink);
		border-bottom-color: var(--ink);
	}

	.aside {
		grid-area: aside;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
		border-left: 1px solid var(--rule);
		max-width: 24rem;
		align-self: end;
	}

	.aside-label {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: var(--step-0);
		color: var(--accent);
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
	}

	.aside-body {
		font-size: var(--step--1);
		line-height: 1.55;
		color: var(--ink-soft);
	}

	.aside-patron {
		margin-top: 1rem;
		padding-top: 1rem;
		border-top: 1px dashed var(--rule);
		font-size: var(--step--1);
		line-height: 1.55;
		color: var(--ink-soft);
		font-feature-settings: "ss01" 1;
	}

	.aside-patron a {
		color: var(--accent);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
		transition: border-color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out);
	}

	.aside-patron a:hover {
		border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
	}
</style>
